# Backend
# Recommended: set these in Vercel Project Settings -> Environment Variables.
# If you omit them, the app will default based on hostname:
# - localhost/127.0.0.1 -> http://localhost:5000
# - otherwise -> https://auto-verse1.onrender.com
# Example:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://auto-verse1.onrender.com/api
# VITE_SOCKET_URL=https://auto-verse1.onrender.com
VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
VITE_SOCKET_URL=http://localhost:5000
